summary.problem: The weekly data for Canadian producer deliveries displayed in the dashboard (SND section) was missing the most recent weeks.
summary.solution: The dashboard data was updated to include the missing weeks. Additionally, the dataset feeding the dashboard is accessible via an API using the dataset code 'thul-c8f165f1-b946-4f05-ac7e-7ee88a902cd1'. Users can run API queries on this dataset using the provided code to retrieve the relevant data programmatically.
